		<credit project="CfPBoK@https://slebok.github.io/cfpbok/"/>
		<h1>Tag <code>T4A</code>: Workbenches</h1>
		All meta-tools, including language workbenches. Work whose primary contribution is meta-tooling for building and using software languages: language workbenches as the most obvious example, but also all other meta-tools, editor and tool integration frameworks, infrastructures for generating or assembling language environments. While language analysis tools can fall into this category, the analyses of language definitions themselves belong in <a href="t5b.html">T5B</a>, and transformation pipelines belong in <a href="t4b.html">T4B</a> or <a href="t4c.html">T4C</a>.
<clear/>
